# Knowledge Base Documents

Place your documents here to be uploaded to the Knowledge Base.

Supported formats:
- Text: .txt, .md, .html
- Documents: .doc, .docx, .pdf
- Spreadsheets: .csv, .xls, .xlsx
- Images: .jpeg, .png

## Usage

1. Add your documents to this directory
2. Run: `./scripts/upload-docs.sh` to upload to S3
3. Run: `./scripts/trigger-ingestion.sh` to process them into the Knowledge Base